      "rationale": "Code verification was performed using method of manufactured solutions for the Navier-Stokes solver. Order-of-accuracy tests confirmed second-order spatial convergence. Required level 4 was set based on MRL 5 expectations; achieved level 3 reflects absence of independent third-party verification."
