      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis damage model was selected based on literature precedent. Sensitivity of hemolysis predictions to model form assumptions was not quantified. Required level 4 is consistent with MRL 5 expectations for absolute prediction contexts. Achieved level 2 because no alternative model forms were evaluated and model-form uncertainty was not bounded."
