      "rationale": "Test sample characterization was not performed. Blood analog fluid properties were assumed from prior studies without independent measurement. Required level 3 is standard for this factor at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 because no sample-specific characterization data were available and inter-batch variability was not assessed."
    },
