    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below required levels, the assessment team accepted the simulation evidence on the basis that Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification bounds remain below the clinical hemolysis threshold with 90% confidence. The team noted that several requiredLevel values were set without documented acceptanceCriteria, meaning the basis for those thresholds cannot be independently verified. This gap was acknowledged but not resolved prior to the decision.",
